dc_description_s: This data represents zoning for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2023 and includes the layers 'Polk_General_2023' and 'Polk_Shoreland_2023. General: [Zoning District Map Features are drawn per the CODE OF ORDINANCES Chapter 42 ZONING] Shoreland: [This dataset designates the zoning district for geographical areas in Polk County. The data set is a compilation of multiple interanal data sets including 'ZoningComp', 'ZoningShoreland', 'ZoneGenPur', and 'ZoningWet'. CODE OF ORDINANCES Chapter 42 ZONING]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.polkcountywi.gov/government/divisions_and_departments/environmental_services_division/land_information/gis_data_portal.php
